@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";  // Assuming you're using a layout file
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IIIT Kottayam</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0d1117;
            color: #f0f6fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .background-text {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #00ffcc;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .section-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #00ffcc;
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #ff6ec7;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #b0bec5;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            width: 150px; /* Set a specific width */
            height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.5);
        }

        a.btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            margin: 10px 5px 0 0;
            border: 2px solid #00ffcc;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #00ffcc;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1em;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        a.btn:hover {
            background-color: #00ffcc;
            color: #0d1117;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Experion Experience Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="background-text">EXPERIENCE</div>
            <div class="section-content">
                <h1>Indian Institute of Information Technology</h1>
                <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ajith0004/Portfolio/825024d0f00bb3d2a5e61a21454bf4aad79ba8d6/logo.jpg" 
                     alt="Indian Institute of Information Technology" />
                <h2>Research Intern</h2>
                <p>During my internship at the Indian Institute of Information Technology, Kottayam, I gained hands-on experience in network security using Cisco Packet Tracer. I explored key areas such as configuring encryption protocols, setting up firewalls, and implementing intrusion detection systems. My work included simulating various cyber-attacks (e.g., ARP spoofing, DHCP spoofing) and designing defensive mechanisms to secure wireless networks. I also learned to analyze and mitigate risks, ensuring network confidentiality, integrity, and availability. This experience provided me with a solid foundation in cyber security, enhancing my skills in threat analysis, network configuration, and practical problem-solving in a simulated environment. </p>
                    
                <div class="section-content">
                    <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")" class="btn">Go Back</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>